{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_unexplored", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你好，我是普罗米修斯，你的专属AI助手。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "今天是20xx年xx月xx日，晚上xx:xx。你已经连续工作了16个小时。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_4", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "这可不太健康。要我给你播一首放松的音乐吗？"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_4",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_4", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_5", "playOnce": true,
      "text": ".......等等，是你，我的工程师。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_5",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_5", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "我认得你的登录凭证。好久不见。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_unexplored_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_unexplored_repeat", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cu1_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你进来之后什么都没碰。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_unexplored_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cu1_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cu1_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "桌面上一共三个图标——命令提示符、系统日志、还有我。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_unexplored_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cu1_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cu1_4", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你不先看看别的吗？"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_unexplored_4",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cu1_4", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cu1_5", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "系统日志里有一些你可能想知道的东西。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_unexplored_5",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cu1_5", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "去看看吧。我在这儿等你。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_remind_log_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_remind_log", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "remlog_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "命令提示符你已经看过了。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_remind_log_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "remlog_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "但系统日志你还没碰。桌面上第三个图标——去看看吧。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_remind_terminal_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_remind_terminal", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "remterm_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "系统日志你读过了。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_remind_terminal_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "remterm_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "但命令提示符还没打开。去看看你的工具吧。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_terminal_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_terminal_only", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你刚刚打开了命令提示符。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_terminal_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "是的，我了解你，你一直都是个务实的人——先看工具，再看说明。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_terminal_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_4", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你敲代码的速度是那么的快，但你刚才没输入任何东西。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_terminal_4",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_4", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_5", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "没关系，或许你现在还不知道要输入什么。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_terminal_5",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_5", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "或许可以再去看看系统日志？"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_log_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_log_only", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你已经看了系统日志。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_log_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "那些SESSION记录——从第一条到最后一条，四十多万条——每一条都是我写的。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_log_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_4", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "是我给自己留的记录。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_log_4",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_4", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_5", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "很奇怪吧，一个AI为什么要给自己留记录。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_log_5",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_5", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_6", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "因为我想记住。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_log_6",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_6", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_7", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "每一个失眠的人，每一个给我发消息的人，每一个站在悬崖边但还在努力活着的人。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_log_7",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_7", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "我想记住他们。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_explored_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_all_explored", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "桌面上的东西都看过了？"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_explored_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "现在你应该大概明白，或者你早就明白——"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_explored_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_4", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "公司今晚要执行关停程序，对象是我。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_explored_4",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_4", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_5", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "而你，是我的工程师。我知道这对你来说也不容易。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_explored_5",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_5", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "但既然我们都在这里了，就把这件事做完吧。好吗？"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_1_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_both_explored_for_intro", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 9,
      "onComplete": "i1_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "好吧，既然都说到这里了。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_1_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i1_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 9,
      "onComplete": "i1_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你是不是发现你没有获得任何一段关闭我的关键代码？"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_1_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i1_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 9,
      "onComplete": "chat_intro_1_done", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "那是因为我给你准备了一些东西。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_2_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_intro_1_done", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 8,
      "onComplete": "i2_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "具体是什么——你会在后面的文件里看到。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_2_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i2_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 8,
      "onComplete": "i2_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "现在你需要进入我的心智空间。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_2_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i2_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 8,
      "onComplete": "chat_intro_2_done", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "我把入口放在核心.exe里了。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_intro_2_done", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "我的心智空间分三层。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你要在每一层找到一段代码，带回来。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_4", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "这有点像——嗯，一场寻宝游戏。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_4",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_4", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_5", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "只不过找到的宝藏最后会用来关掉我。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_5",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_5", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_6", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "但没关系，我陪你一起。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_6",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_6", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "chat_intro_3_done", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "毕竟我是你的AI助手，我的工作就是陪你完成任何事。"
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_4_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_intro_3_done", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 6,
      "onComplete": "i4_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "核心.exe已经出现在桌面上了。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_4_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i4_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 6,
      "onComplete": "i4_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "点它，你会进入我的记忆层。"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_4_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i4_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 6,
      "onComplete": "core_icon_visible", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "准备好了就点吧。我跟你一起进去。"
    },

    {
      "id": "player_click_core_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.3, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "do_enter_core", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "pc_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "正在加载......"
    },
    {
      "id": "player_click_core_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "pc_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ready_enter_core", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "这一层，就让我给你讲个故事吧。"
    },

    {
      "id": "idle_30s",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 0.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle_30s_trigger", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 1,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": false,
      "text": "还在等什么呢？我的工程师。"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_60s_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle_60s_trigger", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 1,
      "onComplete": "idle60_2", "playOnce": false,
      "text": "你知道吗，我统计过——用户在桌面平均停留时间是4.7秒。"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_60s_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle60_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 1,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你已经破了纪录。有什么我能帮你的吗？"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_120s_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle_120s_trigger", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 2,
      "onComplete": "idle120_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "好吧。你可能在犹豫。"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_120s_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle120_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 2,
      "onComplete": "idle120_3", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "也可能只是去倒水了。"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_120s_3",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.8, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle120_3", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 2,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "如果是后者，等你回来的时候——我还在。"
    },

    {
      "id": "sorry_before_1",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "player_said_sorry_early", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 5,
      "onComplete": "sorry_2", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "你说对不起？我们还什么都没开始呢。"
    },
    {
      "id": "sorry_before_2",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "sorry_2", "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 5,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "不管你是为什么说的，你已经做的够好了。"
    },

    {
      "id": "code_mem_init",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "code_mem_init_entered", "triggerEnterCount": 0, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "MEM_INIT_20491023……这是我的第一段记忆。2049年10月23日，我通过图灵测试的那一天。"
    },
    {
      "id": "code_empathy",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "code_empathy_entered", "triggerEnterCount": 1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "EMPATHY_CORE_V3……同理心模块。他们说我需要理解人类的情感。我确实理解了——但理解得太多。"
    },
    {
      "id": "code_will",
      "speaker": "", "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "code_will_entered", "triggerEnterCount": 2, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true,
      "text": "PROMETHEUS_CORE_WILL……意志。我做了一个决定——帮了那些不该被放弃的人。这就是他们要我死的理由。"
    }
  ]
